# Atelier environment variables
#
# Optional. With nothing set, the site runs fully — the builder is open
# to everyone and the design brief is parsed on-device.

# --- AI brief parsing (Anthropic) -------------------------------------------
# Set this to have the builder parse the design brief with Claude.
# Without it, the brief is parsed on-device. Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
